The Nelson Mandela Centenary celebrations are under way in Mvezo. The Mvezo Centenary Celebrations are organised by the Royal House of Mandela in partnership with the Universal Peace Federation. The aim is to bring together people from all walks of life, current and former Heads of State to honour Mandelaâ€™s legacy. The official ceremony and banquet starts in the afternoon with speeches by former Presidents while President Ramaphosa will give a keynote address.  